<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.3.7">
<l>māṟṟa māva titta ṉaiyē vammi ṉarakkaruḷḷīr</l>
<l>cīṟṟam nummēl tīra vēṇṭil cēva kampēcātē</l>
<l>yāṟṟal cāṉṟa tolpi ṟappi laṉuma ṉaivāḻkaveṉṟu</l>
<l>kūṟṟa maṉṉār kāṇa vāṭīr kuḻama ṇitūramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Our] reply is namely this: You who are demons, come!</l>
<l>If you want the fury against you to end, without boasting of honor,</l>
<l>Saying, “Hail, Hanumān of ancient birth whose strength is great!”</l>
<l>So that the one who is like Death sees, dance to the kuḻamaṇitūram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
